| *Module 6: A03 Injection \| BBC Academy / JBI Training*               |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+

+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+
| **Levels 1--2:** Your instructor will demonstrate these. Watch what   |
| gets typed into the URL or form field, and look at the page source to |
| understand why it works.                                              |
|                                                                       |
| **Levels 3--5:** Work through these yourself --- use the hints in the |
| table below if you get stuck. Each level introduces a new XSS context |
| that requires a different approach.                                   |
|                                                                       |
| **Level 6:** Expert level. If you reach this in the session ---       |
| excellent. If not, it is an excellent take-home challenge. The        |
| concepts it covers (CSP and dynamic script loading) are the most      |
| important XSS mitigations in modern web development.                  |
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------+

